"dislike":0,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"d59656be9ed62e42af0f6c5c3fbff2957c822e42","tid":1314213,"uid":110880,"like":322,"dislike":1,"score":321,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:45:57.000Z","msg":"當年，我就係嗰6000個其中1個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:01:18.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n(年齡暴露"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53537f96172647a14b08b575fd3372f2aa4570b8","tid":1314213,"uid":278717,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2192566c11508d72d24a9eeb071dabf38a0977c1","tid":1314213,"uid":202516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gyN7fS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gyN7fS.png&h=d69a9272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n六千學生吹笛破紀錄<br />\n2004-12-28<br />\n港 聞<br />\n <br />\n當大會宣布成功刷新健力士世界紀錄時，台下的學生都舉起手中的牧童笛歡呼。　黎樹雄攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n六千多名學生昨日齊齊吹奏牧童笛，刷新健力士世界紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】六千二百四十三名中、小學生昨在灣仔會展中心齊齊用牧童笛一口氣吹奏《JingleBells》、《普世歡騰》等五首歌曲，笛聲清脆，場面壯觀；當大會宣布他們成功刷新健力士世界紀錄中最多人一齊吹牧童笛的紀錄時，大家都揮動手上的牧童笛慶祝一番。 <br />\n多位學生說，參加旨在為港增光，故在十月時收到樂譜後即開始積極練習；其中在灣仔聖若瑟小學就讀的羅羲和說：「我覺得成功感大過考第一。」 <br />\n該活動由恒生銀行主辦，為香港管弦樂團的學生票資助基金籌款，每名參加者至少捐出二十元，連同恒生的捐款，昨日共籌得三十萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"一齊吹簫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106f23c340d7531827fe1a0c60438ff7c970debe","tid":1314213,"uid":223491,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"01fe2c0da9587f46ce009d8a4c57bf517b5777de","tid":1314213,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1f0f505291bd5d43ed0870d253b7d86a6b1cfd8","tid":1314213,"